{"tid":696233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(法律jj求問)我朋友既親戚想分曬佢老豆既遺產","createTime":"2018-06-10T01:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T07:11:03.000Z","uid":162765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec4fd2c0bc4ac093a29d503f59822eb456a76ff","tid":696233,"uid":162765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T01:55:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n我朋友老豆早幾日過身 咁佢老豆生前就玩開錶 同錢幣 都值幾百萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁佢老豆過身個日 佢d親戚就話幫佢整後事手續 拎曬佢d臨時死亡證 同身份證咁 個時我朋友好傷心  喊到企唔穩 <br />\n<br />\n點知第二日佢幾個親戚就上去佢屋企拎野 話驚比人拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢地話驚有人黎偷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（我朋友阿公有佢屋企條匙 佢比地左佢地）<br />\n<br />\n咁我朋友想拎返 但佢地話要用黎比老人家養老<br />\n<br />\n我朋友都知財到光棍手 咩撚野都無架啦<br />\n<br />\n但而家仲有一筆公司既強積金同保險 我想問咁到時可以點拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都知搵律師問會可靠d 但想問一問有個了解先 唔該咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d5debf8bed1cdad3edd2bc5b323ba945d1c330","tid":696233,"uid":35021,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"報警同搵律師"},{"pid":"38e68897f7c789d2a4b6846c7cea6a23c347c923","tid":696233,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:02:54.000Z","msg":"有無平安紙先"},{"pid":"6e3363f1999634b05b2c0afe35b9dbb2f5ff9fcf","tid":696233,"uid":27416,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚兒戲既咩<br />\n幾百萬野任人拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e778f691d1ea7ee70145ddfb9b19d0f24c14508","tid":